data.Name: Kirby Dominant
data.Bio: Kirby Dominant is a Grand Master of "Fresh 'N Free" style of rap that is gaining popularity in rural malls all over America. Parents feel safe allowing their 9-11 year old children to listen to him nonsensical silly rhymes. Like a step up from Barney or Sesame Street, this is a nice, safe alternative to "true" "gangstas" such as 50-cents and Snoopy Dog. Read more on Last.fm
